doc.title: Uhlolojikelele lwe-Link Open With extension
doc.description:
Lesi sandiso sikuvumela ukuthi ulawule kalula ukuthi izixhumanisi zivulwa kanjani.

Iwindi: ezinye iziphequluli, amawindi ezigelekeqe, amawindi amasha, amawindi e-incognito amasha, iwindi lamanje (okuzenzakalelayo)

Amathebhu: kwesokunxele sethebhu yamanje, ithebhu yamanje, kwesokudla sethebhu yamanje (okuzenzakalelayo)

Isimo sokwenza kusebenze: akusebenzi, yenza kusebenze ngokushesha (okuzenzakalelayo)
